      <h2>Why book direct</h2>
      <ul class="legal-page__list">
        <li>Speak straight with AA Residency for room availability and special requests.</li>
        <li>Transparent indicative rates displayed on our site — final rates are confirmed with you before arrival when applicable.</li>
        <li>
