    <div class="legal-page__block">
      <h2>Enquiry vs confirmed reservation</h2>
      <p>
        Submitting the online <a href="/Booking.html">booking request form</a> creates an <strong>enquiry</strong>. Our team reviews dates, room type, and occupancy,
        then contacts you (typically by phone, WhatsApp, or email) to confirm availability and next steps.
      </p>
      <p>A booking is treated as <strong>confirmed</strong> only after the hotel communicates confirmation and any deposit or identification steps agreed between you and the hotel.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-page__block">
      <h2>Rates &amp; taxes</h2>
      <p>
        Published room tariffs on our site include applicable taxes unless we state otherwise in writing for your specific dates or offer.
        If you need a formal quote or invoice format, mention it when our team confirms your reservation.
      </p>
      <p class="legal-page__rates-inline">
        Indicative tariffs on the booking page reflect pricing current as of
        <time datetime="{{ siteContext.ratesEffectiveISO }}">{{ siteContext.ratesEffectiveLabel }}</time>. Seasonality and demand can change what applies to your stay — ask when you confirm.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-page__block">
      <h2>Payments &amp; security</h2>
      <p>
        This website does <strong>not</strong> collect card numbers through the enquiry form. If payment is requested, staff will advise approved methods 
        such as bank transfer or a secure payment link provided by recognised providers.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-page__block">
      <h2>Check-in / check-out &amp; ID</h2>
      <p>
        Guests should carry valid government-issued photo identification as required under local regulations at check-in (for example Indian nationals with Aadhaar or passport as applicable;
        foreigners with passport and visa arrangements per current norms). Approximate timings are communicated at confirmation stage; flexibility may depend on housekeeping and arrivals.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-page__block">
      <h2>Cancellations &amp; date changes</h2>
      <p>
        Fair cancellation or modification rules depend on how close your stay is, seasonality, channel of booking (direct vs OTAs where applicable),
        and any deposit taken. Ask our team when you confirm for the wording that applies to <em>your</em> reservation.
      </p>
    </div>

